      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-compression forged internals. This unit has received comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a bulletproofed double-VANOS system. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise shifts, sending power to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally pristine, with documented rear subframe reinforcement and factory-spec bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. The exterior finish remains in showroom condition, free of oxidation or road rash, while the interior retains its original tactile integrity. A mechanically unmolested, turnkey machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
